Command Prompt commands to install and configure Django:
pip install Django
django-admin startproject PROJECT_NAME
cd PROJECT_NAME
python manage.py startapp webapp

Inside of the "INSTALLED_APPS" list in settings.py for the Django project, add the app:
INSTALLED_APPS = [
    'django.contrib.admin',
    'django.contrib.auth',
    'django.contrib.contenttypes',
    'django.contrib.sessions',
    'django.contrib.messages',
    'django.contrib.staticfiles',
    'webapp'
]

To run the server:
python manage.py runserver
